---
title: Caribbean-Spiced Chicken & Roast Potato Chunks with Charred Corn Rainbow Slaw
description: We're using our mild Caribbean jerk seasoning to give the classic combo of chicken and roasted potatoes some Jamaican mojo. A colourful slaw with charred corn brings added excitement to this devilishly delicious dish.
